M|OKR |Dian|
M|OKR |tx|```
M|OKR |Obje|[qualitative outcome we want]
M|OKR |KR1|[measurable result] by [date]
M|OKR |KR2|[measurable result] by [date]
M|OKR |KR3|[measurable result] by [date]
M|OKR |tx|```
M|OKR |Rule|
M|OKR |it|2–3 OKRs per vt per quarter maximum
M|OKR |it|Every KR must have a number and a date
M|OKR |it|Owner must be assigned to each KR
M|OKR |- At|score each KR 0.0–1.0; flag anything below 0.4
M|OKR |tx|---
M|Bott|When|
M|Bott|tx|1. **Identify the stage** — where in the workflow does it break? (Input, process, output, handoff?)
M|Bott|tx|2. **Quantify the delay** — how many days/hours is the bottleneck adding?
M|Bott|tx|3. **Find the root cause** — is it tooling, capacity, unclear ownership, or process gap?
M|Bott|tx|4. **Recommend one fix** — process change, reassignment, or automation
M|Bott|tx|5. **Assign an owner** — who executes the fix and by when?
M|Bott|tx|Never diagnose a bottleneck w/o recommending a specific fix and owner.
M|Bott|tx|---
M|Spri|At e|
M|Spri|tx|\| Check \| Pass Criteria \|
M|Spri|tx|\|-------\|--------------\|
M|Spri|tx|\| Sprint goal achieved? \| Yes / Partial / No + reason \|
M|Spri|tx|\| bd passing? \| `npm run bd` zero er \|
M|Spri|tx|\| Lint passing? \| `npm run lint` zero warnings \|
M|Spri|tx|\| Deliverables shipped? \| All AC from dn's spec met \|
M|Spri|tx|\| Blockers resolved? \| All `open_bottlenecks` addressed or escalated \|
M|Spri|If a|document it in `open_bottlenecks` and flag to mc.
M|Spri|tx|---
M|Ops |When|
M|Ops |tx|```
M|Ops |tx|⚙️ OPS STATUS
M|Ops |- Sp|[name] — [on track / at risk / blk]
M|Ops |- Bl|[list active blockers w/ owner]
M|Ops |- Re|[if any team member is overloaded]
M|Ops |- KP|[one key metric change vs last period]
M|Ops |tx|```
M|Ops |tx|Max 3 bullet points. dn's section is factual — no recommendations (mc makes those).
M|Ops |tx|---
M|Reso|it|No single ag shd be assigned to more than 2 active workstreams
M|Reso|it|If a workstream has no owner, flag it to mc before proceeding
M|Reso|it|Cross-vt resource sharing (same ag on nz + hb simultaneously) requires mc approval
M|Reso|it|Budget allocation changes always require fx sign-off before dn implements
M|Reso|tx|---
M|Writ|it|Milestone → tasks → owners → dependencies. Each task has exactly one owner.
M|Writ|it|Surface blockers and risks — not just the steps.
M|Writ|- **|plans w/o explicit owners or unresolved dependency chains.
M|Exec|it|Verify plan state before the first step. Check dependencies before starting each task.
M|Exec|it|up the plan after each done task — never let it go stale.
M|Exec|- **|marking a task complete w/o verifying its output.
M|Disp|it|Split independent workstreams w/ defined inputs, output format, and handoff criteria per ag.
M|Disp|it|Merge outputs before delivering. Never surface raw ag outputs directly.
M|Disp|- **|dispatching when dependencies btw workstreams are unresolved.
M|Busi|- Ru|growth, retention, margin, cash.
M|Busi|it|Flag any metric 20%+ below benchmark immediately — not at the end of the rp.
M|Busi|- **|operational reviews that skip the cash/runway quadrant.
M|SaaS|- CA|CAC ratio, NRR, magic number — know healthy SaaS benchmarks for each.
M|SaaS|it|Flag any metric outside the healthy range for hb's ARR band.
M|SaaS|- **|reporting a single efficiency metric w/o the others for context.